column1: # Supplemental File S5 - Canonical Sub-Genomic RNA Counts From In Vitro Illumina Metagenomic Data
# Canonical ORF counts of sub-genomic RNA from an in vitro model of SARS-CoV-2 infection assayed using Illumina metaganomic methods
# amplicons: The amplicon(s) that gave rise to the sub-genomic RNA
# sgRNA_count: The number of sub-genomic reads at this ORF
# coverage: Average coverage in a wiondow around ORF start site
# sgRPTL: Sub-genomic reads per thousand around ORF start site (coverage)
# sgRPHT: Sub-genomic reads per hundred thousand mapped reads
